Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,和我联手吧  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:08.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,第四名？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:12.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的为人真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大包是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:17.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我的房间  就让我自己来挑选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,至于房间我也有一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我应该和士郎在同一房间内就寝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  住下了是怎么回事啊  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样只会被其他的Master给杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:33.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,职位是Assassin之Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:40.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fnsimhei}Assassin{\fn方正隶变简体}：暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:40.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我服了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,既然对方报上姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也要报上姓名才符合骑士的礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫小次郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Assassin之Servant  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:11.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你是知道对方名字就不得不作出回应的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  不解风情的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真名什么的不知也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对吾等而言  用刀剑来理解敌人就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant本来就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是吗  Saber之Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  决斗吧Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？胸口好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,果然难以对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到无形之剑居然如此麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我的剑法是邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:00.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是泛泛之辈  第一击就能取下其首级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,而你竟然能坚持这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  不可能这样就结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不可视之剑  又并非虚有其表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你要嘴硬到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,目测到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:26.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,刀长三尺多  宽度约四寸左右吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:41.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不使用任何魔术  也没有确实地交锋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就推测出了剑的形态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,时机已成熟了  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你也差不多该停止隐藏实力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我对你并没有使出全力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,难道使出了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想做何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但把剑收在鞘中战斗着实是在藐视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  那么到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:15.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你舍不得出手  就先让你见识一下吾之秘剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,架起剑来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,否则会死的  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,秘剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,燕返
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  躲过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,还真了得呢  你的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:26.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,以Saber为诱饵  然后潜入我的阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:32.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是按照Master所指的方针行事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,若是三骑士之Servant的话那还不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}三骑士之Servant：指Saber，Lancer和Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:09.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但对付Rider我可不会落后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:34.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,燕子感受到大气的震动而改变飞行的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那么只要封住退路就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,第一刀压制住燕子  然后另一刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,封住以风力闪避的燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不过它们很灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,成败与否几乎是在一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:54.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,两刀几乎同时挥过去才可以  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的剑并不是如此简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一瞬间  的确存在着两把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,多重次元曲折现象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没有使用任何魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只以剑技就达到了宝具的领域…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里的立足点很差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,燕返本来有三条轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方如果再稍微宽阔一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就能把侧面的一击也补上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,吾曾因被召唤到这俗世而诅咒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但也到今晚为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,若能实现生前所得不到的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:50.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情地挥舞秘剑  并相互厮杀的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那就有被召唤出来的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:12.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确不是我能保留实力应战的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:23.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,终于打算认真起来了吗  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:49.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,能承受得了我的一击吗  Assassin之Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:28.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:36.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  宛若台风一般呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可能仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识一下其中隐藏着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,接近不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:02.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这莫非是…  Saber的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:09.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样  连身体都还没有痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:28.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就到此为止吧  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:49.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,有不速之客想要窥视你那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去就不只是我们的决斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:54.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不打算分出胜负吗  Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想越过这道山门的话  我会和你决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  不巧的是我的任务也仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:11.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这里出现碍事的人  对你来说不也是个侥幸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧  有人来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在偷觑的不速之客将目标转为那小子之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:25.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:32.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看你睡得这么安稳  什么话都说不出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  在这里做那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么意见  请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  不是这样  完全不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想把Saber带到  不…搬到房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  刚才根本就是完全不明白的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber独自一人去迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,而士郎是去阻止她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我把她送到房间里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎帮我泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们的故事有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,茶具我已经带来了  在炉灶的右边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:34.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  过来一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,好  马上就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  不是睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才醒过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:53.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,身体自己停止了机能而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不会睡太久的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber  为什么要那样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:12.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我奔赴柳洞寺  和Assassin之Servant战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:16.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为注意到第三名Servant的存在  战斗中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:21.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我想问的是为什么你要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant要战斗是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:29.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,身为Master的你  为什么会叫我不要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:36.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的以为这样做就能在圣杯战争中活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:46.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以让女孩子受伤  身为男人不能袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:50.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想把身为武者的我看作是女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,请更正您刚才所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然Saber说不定是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不要总是在一些小事上纠缠  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在一些小事上纠缠的不正是您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  与其要你来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不如由我自己来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎的防御形同虚设  就如同一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚说的好过分啊  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你太瞧不起Servant了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想以人身打倒英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你在自以为是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不对哦  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎并没有瞧不起Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙只是单纯地讨厌你受到伤害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有这回事  我并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也是知道赢不了Servant的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让Saber受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  即便不可能赢也要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,知道赢不了还是想要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:58.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那结果是自己死掉也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:06.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,比起自己来  这家伙更加重视他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我允许你战斗  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有我自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,所以问你是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,剑术的修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:32.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是在士郎闲暇的时间  我就教你剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:37.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你认同这点的话  我也将认同你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  以后我也可以战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧  即使你教了士郎剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,他依然不可能与Servant匹敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,总比一无所知要来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在战斗时不会迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:57.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  就是赌在士郎本人的决意上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是悠闲地玩过家家的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,要让士郎体会一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不止一次  只要时间许可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就不断让士郎体验到战斗而死的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,让他习惯战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎也请去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,明天在道场会流很多汗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:31.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你让她动真格的了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在发火吗  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:45.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  既然是已经决定了就认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你料理后事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:49.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:04.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0,0,0,,与其要你来战斗  不如由我自己来战斗
